name: Zenline
tag_list: apple-laptops, used-mac, used-apple, laptops, computers, apple, mac, refurbished, macbook
overview:
Zenline sells used and refurbished Apple Laptops including MacBook, MacBook Pro, PowerBook, and iBook and all come with fast free shipping. Their certified used laptops and refurbished Macs are the best laptops for sale at a fraction of their original cost. Every used laptop sold undergoes a thorough certification and reconditioning process in preparation for sale. Plus, all laptops come with a minimum 30-Day warranty and extended service and support programs are available.

Zenline offers replacement batteries and power adapters, laptop parts, and accessories at low prices. Their laptop repair service, for out-of-warranty laptops, is designed to save customers time and money. They can help extend the life of your current Mac or offer you a discount on your purchase of one of their refurbished apple laptops.

Zenline alo buys Apple laptops in any condition or quantity and provides customers a trade in discount for their used laptop.
